{"data":[{"name":"87:1","price":"1. (நபியே!) மிக மேலான உமது இறைவனின் திருப்பெயரை நீர் புகழ்ந்து துதி செய்வீராக;","arabic":"سَبِّحِ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5949,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"sabbiḥi is'ma rabbika al-aʿlā ","translations":["Glorify","(the) name","(of) your Lord","the Most High","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["sabbiḥi","is'ma","rabbika","al-aʿlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,1280],[3,1280,2150],[4,2150,3995]]}},{"name":"87:2","price":"2. அவனே (எல்லா படைப்புகளையும்) படைத்து, (அவற்றை) ஒழுங்குபடுத்தியவன்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5950,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī khalaqa fasawwā ","translations":["The One Who","created","then proportioned","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","khalaqa","fasawwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1020],[2,1020,1680],[3,1680,2915]]}},{"name":"87:3","price":"3. அவனே (அவற்றுக்கு வேண்டிய சகலவற்றையும்) நிர்ணயம் செய்து, (அவற்றை அடையக் கூடிய) வழிகளையும் (அவற்றுக்கு) அறிவித்தான்.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5951,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhī qaddara fahadā ","translations":["And the One Who","measured","then guided","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhī","qaddara","fahadā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1840],[3,1840,2915]]}},{"name":"87:4","price":"4. அவனே (கால்நடைகளுக்கு) மேய்ச்சல் பொருள்களையும் வெளிப்படுத்துகிறான்.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِيٓ أَخۡرَجَ ٱلۡمَرۡعَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5952,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhī akhraja al-marʿā ","translations":["And the One Who","brings forth","the pasture","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhī","akhraja","al-marʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2600],[2,2600,3310],[3,3310,4535]]}},{"name":"87:5","price":"5. பின்னர் அவற்றை உலர்ந்த சருகுகளாக ஆக்குகிறான்.","arabic":"فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحۡوَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5953,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fajaʿalahu ghuthāan aḥwā ","translations":["And then makes it","stubble","dark","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fajaʿalahu","ghuthāan","aḥwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,3780],[3,3780,4795]]}},{"name":"87:6","price":"6, 7. (நபியே! இந்த குர்ஆனை) நாம் உமக்கு ஓதக் கற்பிப்போம். அல்லாஹ் நாடினாலே தவிர, (அதில் எதையும்) நீர் மறக்க மாட்டீர். நிச்சயமாக அவன் மறைந்திருப்பவற்றையும் வெளிப்படையானதையும் நன்கறிகிறான்.","arabic":"سَنُقۡرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5954,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"sanuq'ri-uka falā tansā ","translations":["We will make you recite","so not","you will forget","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["sanuq'ri-uka","falā","tansā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1330],[2,1330,1980],[3,1980,3675]]}},{"name":"87:7","price":"6, 7. (நபியே! இந்த குர்ஆனை) நாம் உமக்கு ஓதக் கற்பிப்போம். அல்லாஹ் நாடினாலே தவிர, (அதில் எதையும்) நீர் மறக்க மாட்டீர். நிச்சயமாக அவன் மறைந்திருப்பவற்றையும் வெளிப்படையானதையும் நன்கறிகிறான்.","arabic":"إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعۡلَمُ ٱلۡجَهۡرَ وَمَا يَخۡفَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5955,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"illā mā shāa al-lahu innahu yaʿlamu al-jahra wamā yakhfā ","translations":["Except","what","wills","Allah","Indeed, He","knows","the manifest","and what","is hidden","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","mā","shāa","al-lahu","innahu","yaʿlamu","al-jahra","wamā","yakhfā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1230],[3,1230,3290],[4,3290,6380],[5,6380,8130],[6,8130,9020],[7,9020,10030],[8,10030,10670],[9,10670,11645]]}},{"name":"87:8","price":"8. சொர்க்கப் பாதையை நாம் உமக்கு எளிதாக்கித் தருவோம்.","arabic":"وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5956,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wanuyassiruka lil'yus'rā ","translations":["And We will ease you","to the ease","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wanuyassiruka","lil'yus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1510],[2,1510,3285]]}},{"name":"87:9","price":"9. ஆகவே, நல்லுபதேசம் (மக்களுக்குப்) பயனளிக்கின்ற வரை நீர் உபதேசித்துக் கொண்டே வருவீராக.","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5957,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhakkir in nafaʿati al-dhik'rā ","translations":["So remind","if","benefits","the reminder","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhakkir","in","nafaʿati","al-dhik'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,950],[2,950,1300],[3,1300,3070],[4,3070,4835]]}},{"name":"87:10","price":"10. நிச்சயமாக எவர் (அல்லாஹ்வுக்குப்) பயப்படுகிறாரோ அவர், (இதைக் கொண்டு) நல்லறிவை அடைவார்.","arabic":"سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5958,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"sayadhakkaru man yakhshā ","translations":["He will pay heed ","(one) who","fears (Allah)","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["sayadhakkaru","man","yakhshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1660],[2,1660,1900],[3,1900,4095]]}},{"name":"87:11","price":"11. துர்ப்பாக்கியமுடையவனோ, இதிலிருந்து விலகிக்கொள்வான்.","arabic":"وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5959,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wayatajannabuhā al-ashqā ","translations":["And will avoid it","the wretched one","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wayatajannabuhā","al-ashqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2420],[2,2420,4215]]}},{"name":"87:12","price":"12. (எனினும்,) அவன் (நரகத்தின்) பெரிய நெருப்பை அடைவான். ","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يَصۡلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5960,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yaṣlā al-nāra al-kub'rā ","translations":["The one who","will burn","(in) the Fire","[the] great","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yaṣlā","al-nāra","al-kub'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,1680],[3,1680,3400],[4,3400,5055]]}},{"name":"87:13","price":"13. பின்னர், அதில் அவன் மரணிக்கவுமாட்டான்; (சுகமாக) வாழவும் மாட்டான்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحۡيَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5961,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma lā yamūtu fīhā walā yaḥyā ","translations":["Then","not","he will die","therein","and not","will live","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","lā","yamūtu","fīhā","walā","yaḥyā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1650],[2,1650,2180],[3,2180,3100],[4,3100,4010],[5,4010,4740],[6,4740,5865]]}},{"name":"87:14","price":"14. எவர் (பாவங்களை விட்டு விலகிப்) பரிசுத்தவானாக ஆனாரோ அவர், நிச்சயமாக வெற்றி பெற்றார்.","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5962,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qad aflaḥa man tazakkā ","translations":["Certainly","has succeeded","(one) who","purifies (himself)","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["qad","aflaḥa","man","tazakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,350],[2,350,1250],[3,1250,2400],[4,2400,3865]]}},{"name":"87:15","price":"15. அவன் தன் இறைவனின் திருப்பெயரை நினைவு செய்து கொண்டும், தொழுது கொண்டுமிருப்பார்.","arabic":"وَذَكَرَ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5963,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wadhakara is'ma rabbihi faṣallā ","translations":["And remembers","(the) name","(of) his Lord","and prays","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["wadhakara","is'ma","rabbihi","faṣallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1290],[3,1290,2390],[4,2390,3635]]}},{"name":"87:16","price":"16. எனினும், நீங்களோ (மறுமையை விட்டுவிட்டு) இவ்வுலக வாழ்க்கையைத் தேர்ந்தெடுத்துக் கொள்கிறீர்கள்.","arabic":"بَلۡ تُؤۡثِرُونَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5964,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"bal tu'thirūna al-ḥayata al-dun'yā ","translations":["Nay","You prefer","the life","(of) the world","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["bal","tu'thirūna","al-ḥayata","al-dun'yā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,1620],[3,1620,2760],[4,2760,4015]]}},{"name":"87:17","price":"17. மறுமையின் வாழ்க்கைதான் மிக்க மேலானதும் நிலையானதுமாகும்.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ وَأَبۡقَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5965,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ākhiratu khayrun wa-abqā ","translations":["While the Hereafter","(is) better","and everlasting","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ākhiratu","khayrun","wa-abqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1580],[2,1580,3190],[3,3190,4805]]}},{"name":"87:18","price":"18. நிச்சயமாக இது முன்னுள்ள வேதங்களிலும்,","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَفِي ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5966,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna hādhā lafī al-ṣuḥufi al-ūlā ","translations":["Indeed","this","surely (is) in","the Scriptures","[the] former","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","hādhā","lafī","al-ṣuḥufi","al-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1460],[2,1460,2360],[3,2360,2740],[4,2740,3700],[5,3700,4865]]}},{"name":"87:19","price":"19. இப்ராஹீம், மூஸாவுடைய வேதங்களிலும் இருக்கிறது.","arabic":"صُحُفِ إِبۡرَٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5967,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ṣuḥufi ib'rāhīma wamūsā ","translations":["(The) Scriptures","(of) Ibrahim","and Musa","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["ṣuḥufi","ib'rāhīma","wamūsā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,830],[2,830,2360],[3,2360,4025]]}}],"chapter":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la","Chapter Al-A'la","A'la","Surah A'la","Chapter A'la","Al A'la","Surah Al A'la","Chapter Al A'la","Surah 87","Chapter 87","The Most High","الأعلى"],"version":{"key":"tamil_baqavi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ta","version":"1.0.1","last_update":1609966800,"title":"Tamil Translation - Abdulhamid Albaqoi","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Tamil by Sh. Abdulhamid Albaqoi"}}